com.intel.fightclub.dialog.logging.util

Class ObjectPool<E>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.fightclub.dialog.logging.util.ObjectPool<E>

  • @ThreadSafe
public final class ObjectPool<E>
extends java.lang.Object
    A generic, conditionally threadsafe object pool for holding and distributing a set number of objects. The objects that are stored in the pool are not guaranteed to be threadsafe as no guarantee can be made that the objects are immutable. However, access to the pool itself should be threadsafe.
